<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>Classroom Passcode</title>
  <style>
    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
    }

    main {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .passcode-container {
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
      background-color: rgb(235, 189, 5);
      border-radius: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    p {
      font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;
      font-size: 16px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #666;
    }
    .passcode { 
      font-size: 40px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <header>
      <h1>CLASSROOM PASSCODE</h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <p>HSA BELMONT ELEMENTARY SCHOOL</p>
      <p>Dear <%= fullName %>,</p>
      <div class="passcode-container">
        <p>Your passcode is:</p>
        <h2 class="passcode"><%= doorCode %></h2>
        <p>Please keep this information confidential and do not share it with anyone. If you have any questions, please contact IT Department.</p>
      </div>
    </main>
    <footer>
      <p>This is an automated message. This email is sent to <strong><%= fullName %></strong> by IT Department. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>